com.appiancorp.ps.automatedtest.fixture

Class BaseFixture

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.appiancorp.ps.automatedtest.fixture.BaseFixture
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TempoFixture

    public class BaseFixture
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the base class for integrating Appian and FitNesse. This class contains fixture commands which are generic to Appian tests.
